{"tid":2297001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學民三子認罪︱去年6.21包圍警總 黃之鋒周庭林朗彥認煽惑等罪","createTime":"2020-11-23T03:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T03:39:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b205e9a05c3abc2665c9e3428a90606938aec742","tid":2297001,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、前成員周庭及前主席林朗彥被指於去年6.21包圍警總，被控煽惑、組織及參與未經批准集結等罪名。周庭早前已承認參與及煽惑他人明知而參與未經批准集結兩罪，黃之鋒及林朗彥則否認全部控罪，案件原定於今早在西九龍裁判法院開審。惟黃與林在取得法律意見後，今選擇承認部份罪名，而周庭亦確認早前的認罪答辯。<br />\n案件由裁判官王詩麗處理。黃之鋒及周庭皆由資深大律師駱應淦代表，大律師譚俊傑則代表林朗彥。法庭現播放當日案發情況的片段，預計約一小時。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/DVULAK2NORBMHDBTYB72W3I7PI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FDVULAK2NORBMHDBTYB72W3I7PI%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUna3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=8d0e3324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FDVULAK2NORBMHDBTYB72W3I7PI%2F&h=91069ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/DVULAK2NORBMHDBTYB72W3I7PI/</a>"},{"pid":"4a3bfc9a31d03759d45ce1a4327b0cff1a6ea37d","tid":2297001,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQWjGvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQWjGvS.jpg&h=1d8a14ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔公平！反對！冤案！"},{"pid":"99d8b6f70b1cd4cec7a97ed05232a33445e87809","tid":2297001,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"控方指黃之鋒「積極扮演領導角色」，證據包括他一再呼籲警總外的示威者「分批食飯」"},{"pid":"5da3ba1b9e59de89806142cc82df23193f2c1a5b","tid":2297001,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"咁睇黎坐硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348c26eac0ccc93ce719f9a67458b4c7d9fc2336","tid":2297001